io.github.mrblobman.nbt

Class NBTson

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.mrblobman.nbt.NBTson

  • public class NBTson
extends java.lang.Object
    See NBTson.NBTsonBuilder for creating a new instance of this class. NBTson supports reading deserializable and writing serializable objects to ItemStacks. ItemStacks support custom NBT tags where as Entities and TileEntities only handle recognizable NBT tags. See the read(ItemStack, String, Class) for reading a serialized object from an item and write(ItemStack, String, Object) for writing an object to an item.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      static class  NBTson.NBTsonBuilder
      Following the Builder pattern this class is designed for chaining registration calls for all supported serializers and deserializers that will be required by the constructed NBTson instance.

        Read an object from the item at the given key.
        Type Parameters:
        T - the type of the object being deserialized.
        Parameters:
        item - the ItemStack containing the object.
        key - the key that the object was originally written to.
        type - the class of the object to read.
